	ChipMOS Taiwan Shares, or (ii) at least two-thirds of the votes present at the ChipMOS Taiwan Shareholder Meeting attended by holders of at least a majority but less than two-thirds of the issued and outstanding ChipMOS Taiwan Shares, to
	approve and adopt this Agreement, the Bermuda Merger Agreement, and the Merger and the other Transactions, either of which approval shall in addition constitute a majority of the votes present at the ChipMOS Taiwan Shareholder Meeting attended by
	holders of a majority of the issued and outstanding ChipMOS Taiwan Shares, to approve and adopt the capital increase, issuance of new ChipMOS Taiwan Shares and the issuance of the ChipMOS Taiwan ADSs in the Merger.




