	 means the sum of (i) the Cash Consideration,

	plus

	(ii) the product of (x) the
	average closing price for a ChipMOS Taiwan Share on the TSEC for the 10 consecutive trading days ending with the third complete trading day immediately prior to, but not including, the Closing Date, in US$ based on the average closing NT$:US$ buying
	cash rate published by the Bank of Taiwan for those trading days,

	multiplied by

	(y) 18.71.




