	Share
	Repurchase Plan.


	We effected a US$10 million share repurchase program in compliance with Rule 10b5-1 and Rule 10b-18 under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended on August 20, 2012. The share repurchase plan was completed on
	October 12, 2012 and 654 thousand shares were repurchased under the plan. These repurchased shares were retired and cancelled.








