	Third Quarter Financial Update





	Our unaudited consolidated revenue for the third quarter of 2012 was NT$5,139.9 million or US$175.5 million, an increase of 6.4% from the second quarter
	of 2012 and an increase of 15.2% from the third quarter of 2011.







